Analysis
========

This chapter consists of an analysis of the libretto and the music that 
accompanies it. In particular, I will provide background to the text of the 
libretto, for example by describing why the librettist may have chosen certain 
words or phrases. In addition to this, each movement will have the relevant 
bible verses noted in the sidenotes where they apply.

